OL,5, Social services in Wales have forecast 
OL,6, a budget gap of #646m over the next    
OL,7, three years.                           
OL,9,FCouncils, which provide support and    
OL,10,Fcare to communities, have warned that  
OL,11,Fcuts will have to be made unless they  
OL,12,Freceive extra funding.                 
OL,14,FThe Welsh government said it faced an  
OL,15,Fincredibly tough financial situation.  
OL,17,FThe Welsh Local Government Association 
OL,18,F(WLGA) said councils were facing record
OL,19,Flevels of demand in both children's and
OL,20,Fadult services.                        
